THE DOWNLOAD CONTENT HAVE A STRIPPER CONFIG TO FIX 3 ISSUES ON THE MAP (put the .cfg file in addons/stripper/maps folder)
  • Map features:

>>>> ZE_INFECTED_SEWERS_v6_5 <<<<

------------------------------

* Map created by Kagalera *

* Map fixed by Skullz Lev and Nano*

* Map finished by Nano *

= Version 6.5

= 64 slots

= 3 difficulties (4 soon..)

= 3 human items

= 1 zombie item

= Including boss fights and miniboss fights

= Including an admin room

= Including entWatch support

= Including a stripper config (is not packed, it is on the .rar file)

= TIP: Press E to use an item

= TIP: Nades do a lot of damage on boss in hard difficulty (after RAGE MODE)

= TIP: Music volume can be controlled via user music settings

= Have fun!

*Music improvement

*A few changes at boss fight (Normal Mode and Hard Mode)

*New important item for Hard Mode

*Added Mini-bosses for all stages

*Map optimization

*Added a new playermodel skin that is accessible at the skin room

*A few new models for the map

*Hold points changed a bit

*Deleted colorcorrection

*Added some 'cinematic' stuff

*A few new particles and explosions for Hard Mode
